725147f-a.title: Queens: 26th Avenue - 215th Street
725147f-a.text:
215-49 26th Avenue, north side, east of 215th Street,
Bayside, showing the new home of F.A. Tinklepaugh, eastern
representative of the Weil-Kalter Rayon concern. In the back-
ground is Little Neck Bay with several private yachts anchored
offshore.
About 1929
MoClennon
Bayside, Queens
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE
